Title: My Super Bittersweet Sixteen
Plot: Jenna's sixteenth birthday isn't very sweet as she suffers one embarrassing experience after the next. Jenna is still reeling from the aftermath of her house party and dealing with the repercussions of everyone she's alienated. After failing her driving test and getting humiliated in the school cafeteria, Jenna wonders if she can repair her relationships with Matty and Tamara.
ParentalRatingReason: M Sex scenes and offensive language
GuestStars: Mike Faiola, Matthew Fahey, Wesam Keesh, Shelby Young, John W. Lawson, Kevin Ryan
